{"tid":2193814,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"譚文豪促律師會查周浩鼎涉違操守","createTime":"2020-09-08T06:13:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T09:06:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5b55687c2c9c5ac50c2376fdd255e464e1c05130","tid":2193814,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:13:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200908/767ORJGTBRDLTLEMGC6ZIN2HME/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200908%2F767ORJGTBRDLTLEMGC6ZIN2HME%2F&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqDv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=2f0c769e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200908%2F767ORJGTBRDLTLEMGC6ZIN2HME%2F&h=2c3236b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200908/767ORJGTBRDLTLEMGC6ZIN2HME/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n譚文豪促律師會查周浩鼎涉違操守<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/J9OOqyZlQAxGcqQVtlqwSTfLliw=/1306x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/22VIQWGTBRGN5IGXACUCGEDGE4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJ9OOqyZlQAxGcqQVtlqwSTfLliw%3D%2F1306x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F22VIQWGTBRGN5IGXACUCGEDGE4.jpg&h=44c39882&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n譚文豪<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】民建聯立法會議員葛珮帆及周浩鼎，早前引用匿名消息指控高院法官黃崇厚，指對方促藍絲法官說話要小心，司法機構已回覆內容不實，惟兩人仍死咬不放。公民黨立法會議員譚文豪去信香港律師會，查詢身為律師的周浩鼎未經求證下作出指控，是否有違律師操守。而周否認向司法機構施壓，反質疑譚向律師會投訴是打壓。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指法庭被屈 政府無譴責<br />\n<br />\n譚文豪接受查詢時稱，留意到自8月中開始，紅色媒體及保皇黨不斷攻擊司法機構，如包括何俊堯在內的五位法官被點名為「黃官」，令司法機構受壓，譚指周浩鼎本身為律師，但在沒實質證據下藉詞匿名信向司法機構大興問罪之師，而司法機構最終澄清不是事實，譚質問：「作為律師，佢（周）有冇fact check（求證）？求其有封匿名信就要求司法機構交代，唔係低水平到咁呀？」譚稱會去信律師會查詢周此舉是否違反律師操守，又指若以政府不時出稿譴責失實指控時，為何未有出稿譴責製造失實輿論的人及媒體，「點解唔支持吓司法機構？」<br />\n<br />\n周否認施壓，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n左派近日將矛頭指向終審法院首席。。。。。。"},{"pid":"39565955e7096f3eea8b6bafe12c660dac67b13a","tid":2193814,"uid":335434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:34:18.000Z","msg":"何妖過撚份到咁Law Soc都仲未出手啦 頂頂驚都未撚驚過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"366abd82119871ad95cf8bc72fd9f2911facaed8","tid":2193814,"uid":333752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39565955e7096f3eea8b6bafe12c660dac67b13a","tid":2193814,"uid":335434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:34:18.000Z","msg":"何妖過撚份到咁Law Soc都仲未出手啦 頂頂驚都未撚驚過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:37:49.000Z","msg":"打龍通都冇事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f93d82835e67dd65b381e2f966d7faf04f3e086f","tid":2193814,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:38:01.000Z","msg":"Law Soc 做商業case 地產case都搵飽食醉<br />\n操咩守"},{"pid":"6f7b94569892f834864bd63572d258d0d45115e4","tid":2193814,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"366abd82119871ad95cf8bc72fd9f2911facaed8","tid":2193814,"uid":333752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39565955e7096f3eea8b6bafe12c660dac67b13a","tid":2193814,"uid":335434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:34:18.000Z","msg":"何妖過撚份到咁Law Soc都仲未出手啦 頂頂驚都未撚驚過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:37:49.000Z","msg":"打龍通都冇事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:47:21.000Z","msg":"佢大叫「殺無赦」都無事啦<br />\n<br />\n操守？"},{"pid":"6d35e8ba51b22c0f3bfd4420c9341c1d89daa597","tid":2193814,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T08:03:56.000Z","msg":"飛機佬叫唔係omdb叫？"},{"pid":"44e8fa5cd7c2b4cc8601cde7557c4d94363e2fd4","tid":2193814,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T08:0